task.summary: Code cleaning trimming in Playground enhanced readability
Refactoring Snake model created Dissociated Snake and Playground elements created SnakeHost interface that Playground now implements
Refactoring Snake / Playground decoupling Moved getMessagePoints() to PixelNumbers which was more appropriate Removed redundant instructions in snake movement methods
Renaming MyColors is now AppColors SnakeGame is now GameRunner PixelNumbers is now AlphanumericMatrices Removed toString() from ColorPoint
